{"tid":532243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尋舊物","createTime":"2018-01-17T15:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T16:26:06.000Z","uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"742d5ab960d1ba8a39bb093668cf48f6cb5c5ac8","tid":532243,"uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T15:37:09.000Z","msg":"今朝老豆去我房拎野果陣打爛左我一件好有記念價值既擺設<br />\n重趁我未番屋企果陣就清理左現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然重新買果對已經無左原本意思<br />\n但我始終都係想買番隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n件野係一對陶瓷造既接吻魚擺設<br />\n2條魚可以左右拉開佢地, <br />\n佢地就會自動上鏈, <br />\n然後慢慢去番原位<br />\n<br />\n幾年前重係旺角d曬相鋪到賣緊<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打見到邊到有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2手都接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0aecff14bbef59e1b56b756ce9cfc663d8ea61","tid":532243,"uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T17:01:28.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有印象既巴打希望幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c21eb57b21cce0b297fb8a1f4e0ace0fae10e6","tid":532243,"uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:46:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39493803595d929251d8b374bc40ae0b70efb35c","tid":532243,"uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:26:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}